                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17930220-61-defend661 t17930220-61-punish349"></join>
               Death
            </rs>. (Aged 46.)</p>
               <p>Tried by the first Middlesex Jury before Mr. Justice GROSE.</p>
